==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Postaxial
<hw>Post*ax"i*al</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Pref.
<ets>post-</ets> + <ets>axial</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Anat.)</fld>
<def>Situated behind any transverse axis in the body of an animal;
caudal; posterior; especially, behind, or on the caudal or posterior
(that is, ulnar or fibular) side of, the axis of a vertebrate
limb.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

